        "subject": "LU-20103 tests: sanityn execvp fails on declare",
        "message": "LU-20103 tests: sanityn execvp fails on declare\n\nsanityn test_77k, and other tests that use nrs_write_read encounter\n\nrunning as uid/gid/euid/egid 500/500/500/500, groups: 500\n[declare] [-a] [pids_r]\nexecvp fails running declare\n\nissue. This is because execvp treats declare as a executable while\nit is actually a bash builtin cmd.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanityn\nSigned-off-by: Zanhua Huang <zanhua@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: Ia9de1403317545f28b25aa26c6d274aeb6cf74e2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
